description: With the kind of menu you won't soon find outside of the the Caribbean, Tropical Tastin' is here to take the Bay Area by storm.Have you been craving some serious Jerk Chicken or Mahi Mahi? Then this menu is just what you need. There's nothing quite like a meal of perfectly seasoned tropical tastes, made with the real feel of the islands. And with a Cuban Sandwich to make Miami jealous, this is a truck you just can't miss!
name: Tropical Tastin'
